					<div  class="col content content-fullwidth"><div class="syndicate"><h1 id="content" class="page-title">Identifying Financially Sustainable Pricing Interventions to Promote Healthier Beverage Purchases in Small Neighborhood Stores</h1></div><div class="row col-12 dateline">
	<div>
